4th Street, west from 184 West 4th Street near Jones Street, showing the corner of Barrow Street, the south side of Sheridan Square, and Stewart's Cafeteria on the west side of Seventh Avenue South, where the Greenwich Village Theatre used to stand.  This is a night club section of the village.
May 1, 1933

P.L. Sperr
